Bombardier Is Bidding on Qatar Lusail, West Bay Metro Projects

-- B y   A m i r   S h a b a n a
-- 
2011-10-17T14:41:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/bombardier-is-bidding-on-qatar-lusail-west-bay-metro-projects.html
Bombardier Inc. (BBD/B) , the world’s third
biggest maker of commercial aircraft, is bidding for two rail
projects in the Persian Gulf emirate of Qatar, said Mickey
Raviv, director of marketing for the  Middle East .  Bombardier has bid to construct a metro in the newly
planned city of Lusail and expects to find out the outcome of
its offer by the year-end, Raviv told reporters in the capital
Doha today. The company will also bid for a project to construct
a metro in Doha’s West Bay business district, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
